"{\"uid\": \"bbc.com-sport-olympics-articles-ce9zz211zxno\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"This video can not be played  Biles & Chiles bow down for Andrade on podium  US superstar Simone Biles said it was \\\"just the right thing to do\\\" after she and team-mate Jordan Chiles bowed down to Olympic gold medallist Rebeca Andrade after the floor final in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 265, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 58, \"end\": 65, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999908122845, \"rank\": 9.187836765530317e-09, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}, {\"begin\": 77, \"end\": 79, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9978627072838506, \"rank\": 0.0021272391156607266, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 90, \"end\": 102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}, {\"begin\": 168, \"end\": 181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Chiles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\"}, {\"begin\": 219, \"end\": 233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebeca Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\"}, {\"begin\": 259, \"end\": 264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999613465, \"rank\": 3.856115359989527e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles had been hoping to win a fourth gold at these Games but a couple of mistakes meant she had to settle for silver behind the Brazilian.\", \"from\": 267, \"to\": 406, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the 27-year-old, who is the world's most decorated gymnast, was far from disappointed and instead joined Chiles in showing admiration to Andrade in one of the iconic images of these Games.\", \"from\": 408, \"to\": 605, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 554, \"end\": 561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999908122845, \"rank\": 9.187836765530317e-09, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The trio also made history as the first all-black podium in men or women's gymnastics at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 709, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Rebeca's so amazing, she's a queen,\\\" said Biles.\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 760, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's such an excitement to watch and then all the fans in the crowd were always cheering for her, so it was just the right thing to do.\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 898, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was an all-black podium so that was super-exciting for us, but then Jordan was like 'should we bow to her?'\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 1011, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 972, \"end\": 978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6576859732547296, \"rank\": 0.5184962741814741, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"and I was like 'absolutely'.\\\"\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1041, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Andrade, who lost out on the all-around title to Biles last week, appreciated the show of respect, saying: \\\"It was very cute of them.\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1176, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1043, \"end\": 1050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999908122845, \"rank\": 9.187836765530317e-09, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are the world's best athletes and what they did means a lot to me.\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1250, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are always rooting for each other, the final is very difficult for everyone.\\\"\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1331, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles now has 11 Olympic medals after winning team, all-around and vault golds in Paris to go with her floor silver, while she was fifth in the beam final.\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1415, \"end\": 1420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999613465, \"rank\": 3.856115359989527e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles achieves 'more than wildest dreams' in Paris  Top five stories from Paris Olympics day 10  Andrade beats Biles 